sellerAgent.name: Patty Turner with Keller Williams Rockwal

data.description:
New price with a motivated seller so come see this beautiful, charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home featuring a beautiful brick wood burning fireplace,
elegant dining room and large kitchen with ample cabinet space. The primary bedroom hosts a large
walk-in closet, dual sinks, linen closet, jetted tub and separate shower. Come see this well maintained home
located just minutes away from interstate 80, retail stores and Buc-ee's.
